Season trends

Time

The pictures of Weapon-Related and Drug related have similar color patterns which suggests these crimes are taking place together or around the same time. Surprisingly, Mondays and Tuesdays are quiet days for Drug related and Weapon related felony crimes. We see that overwhelming majority of the sex crimes occurs at midnight on all days.
